title: NFL Week 17 Picks with Pete Prisco, Nick Kostos and R.J. White (Football 12/28)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Pete Prisco, Nick Kostos and R.J. White to make picks for the Week 17 slate. They make picks for their locks of the week, including the Panthers-Saints (3:00), Bears-Vikings (6:30) and Jaguars-Texans (12:55). Then they look at other games including Browns-Ravens (18:45), what animal Prisco would be (28:00), Lions-Packers (29:25), Raiders-Chiefs (33:30), Falcons-Buccaneers (37:15), Jets-Patriots (40:30), Bengals-Steelers (44:15), Dolphins-Bills (46:00), Eagles-Redskins (47:50), Chargers-Broncos (50:00), Cowboys-Giants (52:30), Cardinals-Seahawks (53:20), Colts-Titans (54:15), 49ers-Rams (55:00) and their EXOTIC PICKS OF THE WEEK (51:00).
